        "content": "<p>Is there a definition of the \"function\"-property of a relation, in the sense of : <em>\"it associates every instance of the first type to exactly one instance of the second type\"</em>?<br>\nAnd if so, is there a method for turning a <code>rel α β</code> into <code>α → β</code>?</p>\n<p>At the moment I'm using:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">data.rel</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">namespace</span> <span class=\"n\">rel</span>\n\n  <span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">is_function</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"n\">β</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">r</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">rel</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Prop</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n    <span class=\"bp\">∀</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">∃!</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">r</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span>\n\n  <span class=\"kd\">noncomputable</span> <span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">function</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"n\">β</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">r</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">rel</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">r.is_function</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">β</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n    <span class=\"bp\">λ</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">some</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span> <span class=\"n\">rel</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
